### Closira API Test File (REST Client / IntelliJ)

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
# Note: After creating an enquiry, copy the returned job_id (e.g. enq_1234abcd) 
# and use it in the {id} path variables below.
@enquiryId = REPLACE_WITH_JOB_ID

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. Create a New Enquiry (Booking SOP)
POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "customer_name": "Sarah Connor",
  "message": "I would like to book an appointment for tomorrow please."
}

### 3. Create a New Enquiry (Complaint / Escalate automatically)
POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "email",
  "customer_name": "John Smith",
  "message": "This is unacceptable, I demand a refund immediately."
}

### 4. Schedule a Follow-up
# Replace @enquiryId variable at the top with a real ID first
POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry/{{enquiryId}}/follow-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay_minutes": 15,
  "message_template": "Hey, just following up on your request. Are you still interested?"
}

### 5. Manually Escalate an Enquiry
# Replace @enquiryId variable at the top with a real ID first
POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry/{{enquiryId}}/escalate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer became irate on the phone."
}

### 6. Get Enquiry History & Timeline
# Replace @enquiryId variable at the top with a real ID first
GET {{baseUrl}}/enquiry/{{enquiryId}}/history
Accept: application/json
